Privacy Policy for Sohokri App

This Privacy Policy governs the manner in which Sohokri ("we," "us," or "our") collects, uses, maintains, and discloses information collected from users ("you" or "your") of the Sohokri mobile application (the "App"). This Privacy Policy applies to the App and all related services offered by Sohokri.

Information We Collect

User-Provided Information: We may collect personally identifiable information ("PII") from you when you use our App, including but not limited to your name, email address, contact information, and other data that you voluntarily provide.

App Usage Data: We may collect non-personal information about your use of the App, including but not limited to device information, location information, and usage statistics.

How We Use Your Information

Pet Services: We use the information you provide to facilitate the buying, selling, and adoption of pets through our App.

Property Services: We use your information to enable property-related transactions, including buying, selling, and renting properties.

Blood Donation: We use your information to help you find nearby blood donors when needed.

Improvement and Analytics: We may use your information to improve our services, conduct research, and analyze user trends and preferences.

Data Storage and Security

We store all user data securely on AppwriteCloud, and we take reasonable measures to protect your data from unauthorized access, disclosure, alteration, or destruction.

Third-Party Services

The App may use third-party services for various purposes. We do not sell or share your user-generated data with these third parties. However, please note that third-party services may have their own privacy policies and terms of service, which we recommend reviewing.

User Responsibility

Any data or services shared between users on the App are done so at your own risk. We are not liable for any actions, transactions, or consequences that may result from interactions between users.

Children's Privacy

The App is not intended for use by children under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect or maintain PII from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe we have collected information from your child, please contact us.

Changes to This Privacy Policy

We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. We encourage you to review this Privacy Policy periodically.

Contact Us

If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or the practices of the App, please contact us at verygoodrove+contact@gmail.com.
